title: Ep. 716 - Inhumane, But Effective
description:
Biden separates migrant children from their guardians and puts them in cages without social distancing, Meghan Markle wants us to pity her, and the CDC loosens its rules as we approach the one-year anniversary of “15 days to slow the spread.”
